Introduction

Kim Yoo-jin, popularly known as Eugene, is a South Korean singer, variety star, and award-winning actress. She was first known for being a member of the first generation female idol group S.E.S under SM Entertainment. After the group's disbandment in 2002, Eugene focused on acting. She is best remembered for her dramas "Save the Last Dance," "Wonderful Life," and the recent hit "Penthouse."

Eugene is married to actor Ki Taeyoung. Together with their daughter Rohui, they joined the variety show "Return of Superman." They left around 2018.
